<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM1.8.2">
<l>ceṅkama lappūviṟ ṟēṉuṇṇum vaṇṭēpōl</l>
<l>paṅkikaḷ vantuṉ pavaḷavāy moyppa</l>
<l>caṅkuvil vāḷtaṇṭu cakkara mēntiya</l>
<l>vaṅkaika ḷālēvan taccōvaccō</l>
<l rend="indent">vārat taḻuvāyvan taccōvaccō</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>As [your] hair comes to crowd around your coral mouth</l>
<l rend="indent">like bees that drink the honey of the red lotus flower,</l>
<l>coming with hands that hold the conch,</l>
<l rend="indent">bow, sword, club, and discus, Oh! Oh!</l>
<l>having come, fully embrace [me]! Oh! Oh!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
